{"tid":1519792,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"懇請大家要冷靜思考，沒有所謂EndGame，不要把萌芽中的𥌓光扼殺","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:12:16.000Z","uid":19326,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"735d39fa26dcb5401c402f8b244465a3c59f64b9","tid":1519792,"uid":19326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"七月嘅時候，天崎有一句說話好想大家記在心中<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRA34qN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRA34qN.jpg&h=0f7fe801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要冷靜思考對家行動背後嘅目的，三思當中可能會出現嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n走到現在我地得到嘅國際支持同關注並不少，如果就咁樣跌入對家嘅圈套，不幸地損失左大量手足，亦令對家有藉口攻擊我地，我地就白白浪費左呢兩個多月嚟爭取到嘅國際支持同關注，就咁樣輸左，值得嗎？我好希望各位可以冷靜思考<br />\n<br />\n大家講好左一齊贏架嗎？大家要攬炒架嘛？唔係咩？點可以未攬炒就自炒左先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"6c3383e8d89a38291db8bc88a8b3ddb2d337a1a8","tid":1519792,"uid":294250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b21e67f95dfda4fc737371136c35933b4e13e66","tid":1519792,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1917ff0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<sp